name: Rentals United
overview:
Joined inventory of 4 of Europe’s leading privately owned apartment rental companies with a goal of having inventory in one place.

For vacation rental owners they must fill in numerous calendars or rely on channel managers to get their live availabilty out to the world. The way the industry is, no one company wants to share their inventory with others.

Rentals united has developed our database where these 4 main companies have shared over 30,000 properties in one place. This means rental owners only need to fill in one calendar for all companies. A number of other big EU companies have expressed interest in adding their properties to make a pool that will rival inventory airbnb, windu and housetrip.
